# LLM-pipeline docs sync

Ändrar du builder-entry, scaffold, route plan, LLM-input, prompt-static, manifest, autofix/repair/verifier eller finalize: **kod → verifiering → berörda kanoniska docs/dashboard i samma leverans.** Diagram/docs = faktisk kod, inte ambition.

## Alltid när ytan ändras (mappa fil → doc)

| Område | Uppdatera |
|--------|-----------|
| Statisk prompt / monolit | `config/prompt-static/_READ_ME_FIRST.md`, `config/codegen-static-prompt.json` |
| Modeller / phase-routing / budget | `config/ai_models/_READ_ME_FIRST.md`, `manifest.json`; mänsklig guide: `docs/schemas/model-build-profiles.md` |
| Generation / orchestrate / input | `docs/architecture/builder-generation.md`, `llm-input-blocks.md`, `llm-signal-flow.md` |
| Steg 4 / finalize | `docs/architecture/step4-post-generation.md` |
| Builder-ingång / ID | `docs/schemas/builder-entry-contract.md` |
| Scaffold | `docs/schemas/scaffold-contract.md` |
| Roller / signaler | `docs/schemas/llm-role-matrix.md`, `orchestration-signal-contract.md` |
| Restlista / stegfokus | `docs/architecture/README.md` |
| Övrig semantik | Berörd fil under `docs/schemas/` |

## Vid behov

`preview-deploy.md`; `docs/plans/README.md`; `repository-and-platform.md` / `config/README.md`; `manifest.schema.json` om **formen** ändras; dashboard: `domain-map.json`, `config/dashboard/app.py` (översikt), `scripts/scripts_dashboard.py` (pipeline) — delad logik i `scripts/dashboard_shared.py`.

## Principer

Uppdatera bara det som faktiskt bröts; inget brett docs-pass av vana. `app.py` = config/översikt; `scripts_dashboard.py` = pipeline/artifacts.

Terminologi: `terminology.mdc` + `docs/architecture/glossary.md`; tvetydiga ord → § Namnskuggor. Verifiera mot kod innan du skriver om docs. Föredra repo-specifika termer (`orchestrate`, `finalize`, `preview materialization`, `verify`) framför generisk CI/CD-jargong.
